		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I swear, if I say some words the way they are actually spelt, I end up sounding like something between a Scottish and a Cardiff (Welsh) accent. And of course being from the US, I have no accent <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /> (hehe)
